# NetFlow - Know your net, Grow your portfolio

## Overview

NetFlow is an AI-powered web application designed to help real estate investors identify the best cash-flowing rental properties in any market.

Simply enter a ZIP code and your budget. NetFlow instantly returns the top 10 properties ranked by estimated net monthly cash flow.


## Key Features

### Smart Property Search

Input a ZIP code and budget to discover high-performing rental properties.

### Top 10 Ranked Deals

Properties are ranked based on estimated net monthly cash flow.

### Instant Financial Insights

Each property includes:

* Estimated mortgage payment
* Projected rental income
* Net monthly cash flow

### AI-Powered Assistant

* Explains each deal in plain English
* Highlights potential risks
* Evaluates property age and maintenance costs

### Real-Time Analysis

Get instant calculations without manual spreadsheets.



## How It Works

1. Enter a ZIP code
2. Set your investment budget
3. Review the top 10 properties
4. Analyze:

   * Cash flow
   * Rent estimates
   * Risk insights
5. Make confident investment decisions



## Why NetFlow

* Eliminates manual calculations
* Simplifies complex real estate analysis
* Helps identify profitable investments quickly
* Provides AI-driven insights for smarter decisions


## Tech Highlights

* AI-powered property analysis
* Real-time financial modeling
* User-friendly web interface



## Tagline

Know your net, Grow your portfolio.


